name: ShuffleNet v2 for Image Classification
short_description: Efficient image classification using ShuffleNet v2.
full_description: ShuffleNet v2 is a lightweight convolutional neural network architecture optimized for mobile and embedded devices. It builds upon the original ShuffleNet by improving the network architecture for better efficiency and accuracy, making it suitable for real-time image classification tasks with limited computational resources.
keywords: image classification, deep learning, ShuffleNet v2, mobile networks, efficient neural networks
author: Alice Johnson

ai_model.name: ShuffleNet v2
ai_model.description: A lightweight convolutional neural network model designed for efficient image classification on mobile and embedded devices.
